Name: bustard
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: A tiny WSGI web framework
Home-page: https://github.com/mozillazg/bustard
Author: mozillazg
Author-email: mozillazg101@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: bustard
        -----------
        
        |Build| |Coverage| |Pypi version|
        
        A tiny WSGI web framework.
        
        
        features
        ===============
        
        * router
        * orm
        * request and response
        * cookies and session
        * template
        * wsgi server
        
        install
        =============
        
        ::
        
            pip install bustard
            pip install psycopg2      # if you need orm feature
        
        
        usage
        ==============
        
        ::
        
            from bustard.app import Bustard
        
            app = Bustard()
        
        
            @app.route('/')
            def helloword(request):
                return 'hello world'
        
            if __name__ == '__main__':
                app.run()
        
        
